{
  "stem": "17372.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 515.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said that he is going to make a munition factory in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And for this, he need 1,300-- I beg your pardon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I make a mistake. 1,100-- no, it must have been 1,300-- 1,100 people he need for this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was only 700 in the barrack-- 1,200 was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm forgetting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had 700, so another 500.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they started to make lists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this is how the list started to be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've been one of the first on the list because Schindler's-- Schindler like us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He like our music.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took 300 men and 200 women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who made the list?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the-- on, on, on the instruction, probably, from Amon Goeth or Schindler.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took some professional men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it wasn't many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was a lot of bribing there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we've been lucky that we went-- and my brother, with his wife, and my sister, Regina Horovitz, with her husband.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a little boy-- my brother had a little boy, Alex.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my sister had a little boy, Richard Horovitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went on the list also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As you've seen on, on, on the film, how he show-- tried to convince Germans that he got very sensitive shells for guns and that a little hand can go into to clean it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Big hand wouldn't go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He tried to cover them up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyhow, I tell you later on what's happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I've been on the list.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one day, without any warning, they took all the men that-- on the train-- good train that we are going to Brunnlitz, to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But instead, we landed in Gross Rosen, other concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
